	(88,78,'B00RY1Z9NQ','','Thai Tan','Garmin vívofit 2 Activity Tracker, Black','garmin-vívofit-2-activity-tracker','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Garmin Vivofit 2 is a fitness band  similar to the original Garmin Vivofit Fitness Band  that allows users to track their daily activity, the number of calories burned in a day, their heart rates, overall progress, (via the Garmin Connect site that the Vivofit 2 automatically syncs with) and even how well they slept. In addition to all this, the Garmin Vivofit 2 also includes a backlit display, audible alerts and the ability to see when you have been inactive for longer than an hour  the device displaying a lit up bar to help motivate you when this happens. Overall, this device is greatly liked by users, some saying that this device is better than any they have tried before, receiving a total of 4 out of 5 stars.</span></p><p class=\"p1\"></p><ul><li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Track your activity, heart rate, fitness goals and more easily, with this stylish and waterproof fitness band.<br/></span></li><li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Hear audible alerts (in addition to the visual alerts on the band itself), when it is time for you to move, you have reached a goal and more.</span></li><li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Connect with others, track your overall progress, join exciting challenges, stay motivated and more, through Garmin Connect.</span></li></ul><p></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Garmin\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"010-01503-00\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"010-01503-00\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Black\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"0.42 X 0.83 X 8.3 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"2.76 X 2.76 X 5.67 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.06 Pound\"}]',0.00,59.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Garmin-v%C3%ADvofit-Activity-Tracker-Black/dp/B00RY1Z9NQ%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3D