	(98,85,'B017H10NGA','','Jade Cutler','Thync Calm and Energy Wearable','thync-calm-and-energy-wearable','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Thync Calm and Energy Wearable is wearable piece of technology that can actually change how you feel. Using low energy waveforms, Thync Calm and Energy Wearable signals nerves in the head and on the face to either energize or relax the individual who is wearing the device at the time. This then, is great for people who need a little extra motivation to get through a busy day or to make it to the gym, or for people who have had a long and stressful day and need to come home and find a way to wind down and relax; either way, this device certainly sounds as if the benefits it offers are great at either end. Users however, have only given this product 3 out of 5 stars, some claiming that, while great in theory, the device does not work as well as it claims to  some people going further and stating that sometimes they wear the device and do not feel any different at all.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></p><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"></span></p><ul><li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Use the device before bed to help to induce better sleep  thereby waking up feeling more refreshed than ever and ready for the day.</span></li><li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Increase your motivation and energy (or decrease your stress and anxiety levels) by wearing the Thync Calm and Energy Wearable for only ten minutes. <br/></span></li><li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Track your energy, stress levels and sleep patterns all on one device.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></li></ul><p></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Thync\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"THY1000\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"THY1000\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"2.13 X 9.06 X 6.5 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Pac