	(835,148,'B00R56XHI4','','Jade Cutler','Perfect Bake Smart Scale and Recipe App Cook Tool, White','perfect-bake-smart-scale-andrecipe-app-cook-tool','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Perfect Bake Smart Scale and Recipe App Cook Tool is a smart scale that is compatible with iOS and Android devices, that allows users to bake the perfect cake, pastry, brownie, etc, every time! Equipped with an LCD display and including color coded bowls, the Perfect Bake Smart Scale and Recipe App Cook Tool allows users to choose a recipe from the extensive library, scale the recipe to fit their specific pan size or specific desired number of cookies, brownies, etc, scale a recipe if they do not have enough of a single ingredient so that it remains perfectly proportioned and even control portioning as they pour/place their baking mixture into various pans for baking. Additionally, this product will alert users in real time, when they have poured enough of a single ingredient into their mixing bowl, via a quality scale, totally eliminating the need to measure out ingredients. This is really a great product for anyone who loves to bake, is learning to bake or is interested in technology, and even offers an extensive list of both gluten free and vegan recipes, truly catering to everyones baking needs. Overall this product receives 4.3 out of 5 stars on Amazon, and 3.5 out of 5 stars on CNET, with many claiming it works well and does have a large selection of recipes to choose from, however if you wish to add your own favorite recipe you are in for a trying and frustrating experience.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Measures your ingredients in real time, scales recipes if you lack enough of a certain ingredient and even helps with portioning out items for baking.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Compatible with iOS and Android devices.<br/></span></li><li class=\"l