	(836,92,'','','Thai Tan','Viatek Smart Touch Wine Opener','viatek-smart-touch-wine-opener','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Smart Touch Wine Opener by Viatek is a clever wine opening device that allows users to easily open any wine bottle, without the need to struggle  as so many of us often do. All the user must do is place the opener over the bottle (above the cork), twist the handle so that the device is attached to the cork itself, then twist the handle back out, thus bringing the cork with it  simple and easy. Additionally, the Smart Touch Wine Opener is equipped with a specific twist and pull action, ensuring the cork will never break, and even includes a folding handle for compact and easy storage. Overall this is a device that makes the act of opening any wine bottle significantly easier, and receives 4.7 out of 5 stars by users on All Modern, with users claiming it is extremely easy to use and they absolutely love it!</span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Easily removes corks when twisted.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Twist and pull action ensure cork never breaks.<br/></span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Handle folds down for compact and easy storage.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></li></ul>','[{\"key\":\"Dimensions\",\"value\":\"5.5\\\" H x 1.5\\\" W x 1.5\\\" D\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"1.05 lbs\"},{\"key\":\"Product Type\",\"value\":\"Corkscrew\"},{\"key\":\"Finish\",\"value\":\"Black\"},{\"key\":\"Primary Material\",\"value\":\"Plastic\"},{\"key\":\"Product Care\",\"value\":\"Wipe clean with a dry cloth\"},{\"key\":\"Dishwasher Safe\",\"value\":\"No\"},{\"key\":\"Country of Manufacture\",\"value\":\"China\"}]',27.99,27.99,2,'http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=1218672&b=65867&m=11035&afftrack=&urllink=www%2Eallmodern%2Ecom%2FSmart%2DTouch%2DWine%2DOpener%2DSTW01%2DVCPG1003%2Ehtml%3FSSAID%3D1218672%26refid%3DS