	(1050,141,'B01CR8IG62','','Thai Tan','LED Plant Grow Light','led-plant-grow-light','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The LED Plant Grow Light is a light that has been specially designed to help indoor plants grow and thrive when they may need a little extra help to do so. Using only blue and red light (blue 400-470nm and red 610-720nm), because plants dont actually need to full light spectrum to thrive, the LED Plant Grow light is able to synthesize the light plants need most into a single source, helping to peak their photosynthesis and in turn grown and thrive. Additionally, this device is extremely easy to install and use  just plug it in, clamp it onto a nearby stand, then turn it on  outputs only 100 watts and produces very little heat, meaning there will be no burning of fingers if one accidentally touches the bulb. Overall this is a great product that has been designed to take up only a minimal amount of space and can really help to supplement plants that need a little extra help, and receives 4.7 out of 5 stars by users on Amazon, most of whom claim it works really well, is a great size and is easy to use.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Designed to use only the most efficient light wavelengths to produce peak photosynthesis in plants.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">Outputs 100 watts, with very minimal heat. <br/></span></span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Extremely easy to install and use.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></li></ul>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"GTaipe\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"GTaipe-001\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"GTaipe-001\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Black\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"17.72 X 3.15 X 4.72 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"4 X 5.4 X 7.4 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.67 Pound\"}]',29.99,25.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/LED-Plant-Grow-Light-Hydroponic/dp/B01CR8IG62%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB01CR8IG62','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":0,\"counter\":0}]','0','','','','Active','Best LED Plant Grow Light Reviews and Deals','The LED Plant Grow Light is a special light designed to bring indoor plants to their peak of photosynthesis. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews and lowest price on the LED Plant Grow Light.','\"\"',NULL,'2016-05-07 18:07:44','2016-07-18 11:25:29'),
	(1051,121,'B00RVMC58U','','Thai Tan','Eye-Vac Home Touchless Vacuum (EVH-W)','eye-vac-home-touchless-vacuum','<div></div><p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The Eye-Vac Home Touchless Vacuum is a stand alone vacuum that allows users to easily sweep dust, debris and pet hair into its mouth, totally eliminating the need to struggle with using a dust pan ever again. At 1000 Watts, this vacuum is easily able to removed 100% of all the mess you need it to clean, and is even equipped with dual settings: off or always on  allowing users to use the device whenever they need without needing to manually power up each time. However, if one chooses the always on option, there is no need to worry about loud vacuum noises or over use of power, because when not physically in use, the Eye-Vac Home Touchless Vacuum will go into hibernation mode, only acting when it senses debris nearby via the included infrared sensors. Overall, this is a great device that makes cleaning any hard floors easier than ever, and receives 4.4 out of 5 stars on Amazon, with users claiming it works well and takes the hassle out of sweeping, however a handheld vacuum could work just as well.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></p><ul><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">1000 Watts, removing 100% of dirt, dust and pet hair.</span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Includes infrared sensors for automatic vacuum action when you bring debris near. <br/></span></li><li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\"></span><span class=\"s1\">Dual settings: keep turned off when not in use, or set to always on so it is ready to go whenever!</span></li></ul>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"CrowleyJones, L.P.\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"EVH-W\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"EVH-W\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Designer White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"18 X 7 X 12 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"9.8 X 15.6 X 19.9 Inches\"},