	(1313,134,'B019I0CMJO','','Aiza Coronado','MESH Wireless Functional Tag Temperature & Humidity','mesh-wireless-functional-tag-temperature-&-humidity','<div></div><p>MESH is a tool that lets you explore the world of Internet of Things (IoT) using ordinary, everyday objects. MESH has different tags that can be connected to any device. It communicated with the MESH app so you can create your own application to suit your unique need. </p><p><br/></p><p>The MESH Wireless Functional Temperature &amp; Humidity Tag detects a change in temperature and humidity. It can notify you when it reaches a certain temperature or humidity that you have set. This opens a lot of applications. After it checks the room temperature and humidity, you can program it on the MESH app to interact with other apps such as Gmail and IFTTT or smart devices like Philips Hue to automate stuff. </p><ul><li>Not waterproof</li><li>Readings are not accurate when used while charging</li><li>Senses once in a second</li><li>Cover holes on the tags should not be covered</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>Note that this tag doesn\'t measure the actual temperature and humidity, just the temperature/humidity changes. </p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"MESH\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"MESH-100TH\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"MESH-100TH\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"BlueViolet\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"1.89 X 0.94 X 0.47 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"1 X 3 X 4 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.03 Pound\"}]',59.99,59.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/MESH-Wireless-Functional-Temperature-Humidity/dp/B019I0CMJO%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB019I0CMJO','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":1,\"counter\":1,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/MESH-Wireless-Functional-Temperature-Humidity\\/dp\\/B019