	(1536,155,'B004GY5P06','','Aiza Coronado','MudWatt','mudwatt','<div></div><p>The MudWatt is a fun and educational kit that lets your kids use soil micro-organisms to generate electricity. It\'s like growing an organic cell fuel. The bacteria power can light up an LED bulb and run a digital clock. The fun part of this experiment is that it encourages your kids to use different kinds of soil and even food or drinks from your fridge! Yes, no kidding. They can experiment which will give more power output. </p><p><br/></p><p>The MudWatt comes with an app that gives insights about their little mud world. The app displays power, bacteria growth, and even challenges them to unlock an educational comic book. The kit includes:</p><p><br/></p><ul><li>2 power-harvesting graphite disks</li><li>LED blinker board</li><li>digital clock</li><li>graduated container</li><li>nitrile gloves</li><li>20-page educational instruction</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>This MudWatt is cooler than it sounds; it has gotten a 4.8-star rating on Amazon. Parents, kids, and instructors are impressed. Teachers have bought this to use it an experiment in their own classrooms. And so far, the results and the kids\' reactions were amazing.</p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Keego Technologies LLC\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"21\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"MW-1\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"One Size\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"4 X 4 X 4 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"4.1 X 4.1 X 4.2 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\" Pound\"}]',39.99,39.95,1,'http://www.amazon.com/MudWatt-Clean-Energy-living-Classic/dp/B004GY5P06%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB004GY5P06','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"5.00\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":5,\"counter\":21,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/gp\\/product\\/B004GY5P06?tag=ideaing07