	(1562,131,'B0177GW9Z8','','Aiza Coronado','GermGuardian AC9200WCA True HEPA Ultra-Quiet Air Purifier System','germguardian-ac9200wca-true-hepa-ultra-quiet-air-purifier-system','<div></div><p>You no longer have to deal with unwanted odors from cooking, smoking, and from your pets. Or your constant sneezing due to allergies. The GermGuardian AC9200WCA True HEPA Ultra-Quiet Air Purifier System will take care of these things for you. This purifier has a true HEPA filter that can capture 99.97% of germs, allergens, household dust, pet danders, mold spores, and plant pollen. And with this GermGuardian, you are sure that the bacteria and viruses are really eliminated; thanks to its UV-C light technology. </p><p><br/></p><ul><li>Recommended for rooms of up to 378 sq. ft. </li><li>Optional ionizer that boosts allergen control</li><li>Removes allergens as small as 0.3 microns</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>Online reviewers claim that this purifier drove their allergies away. They were happy to say goodbye to sneezes and odors. They also like that it operates quietly. Although it is indeed a little pricey, they say that it\'s worth every penny.</p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Guardian Technologies, LLC\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"AC9200WCA\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"AC9200WCA\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Crystal White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"27 X 17 X 9.75 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"12 X 20 X 29 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"20.35 Pound\"}]',0.00,349.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/GermGuardian-AC9200WCA-Hi-Performance-Ultra-Quiet-Reduction/dp/B0177GW9Z8%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB0177GW9Z8','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"5.00\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4.5,\"counter\":27,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/GermGuardian-AC9200WCA-Hi-Performance-Ultra-Quiet-Reduction\\/d