	(1563,131,'B01F7TRMGI','','Aiza Coronado','Gideon Electronic Plug-in Air Purifier','gideon-electronic-plug-in-air-purifier','<div></div><p>Breathe in fresh and clean air with this Gideon Electronic Plug-in Air Purifier. It rids your air of germs, unwanted odor, bacteria, and pollutants that cause you allergies. Have one in your room or even in your office. With its quiet operation, you\'re sure that it\'ll not interfere with whatever you\'re doing. You can even leave it on at night when you go to sleep. It\'s guaranteed capable of 24/7 operation. </p><p><br/></p><ul><li>Recommended for use in rooms of up to 150 sq. ft. </li><li>1-year manufacturer\'s warranty</li><li>UV bulb and stainless steel filters</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>This plug-in purifier gained the favor of its users on Amazon with a strong 4.7-star rating. According to reviewers, it does everything expected of it and more. It works after plugging in and they have noticed that the air smelled a little &#34;cleaner&#34; even during the first use.</p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Gideon\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"GD-UVSNTZ-01\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"Black\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\" X  X  Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"4.1 X 5.4 X 10.1 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\" Pound\"}]',0.00,39.95,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Gideon-Electronic-Plug-Purifier-Sanitizer/dp/B01F7TRMGI%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB01F7TRMGI','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4.5,\"counter\":308,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Gideon-Electronic-Plug--Purifier-Sanitizer\\/dp\\/B01F7TRMGI?tag=ideaing07-20\"}]','0','','1','','Inactive','Gideon Electronic Plug-in Air Purifier Reviews and Deals','Gideon Electronic Plug-in Air Purifier kills germs and lets you e