	(1564,131,'B00D8Y1YNC','','Aiza Coronado','AeraMax 300/DX95 Air Purifier','aeramax-300-dx95-air-purifier','<div></div><p>The AeraMax 300/DX95 Air Purifier has sensors which automatically detects and purifies the air that you breathe. Its true HEPA filter has been treated with AeraSafe microbial treatment and is guaranteed to remove 99.97% of airborne particles including plant spores, cigarette smoke, dust mites, viruses, germs, and dust mites. </p><p><br/></p><p>For maximum efficiency, the AeraMax has special molds for cold and flu season. We all know this is influenza season, so if you\'re an easy target, make sure that you\'re equipped with AeraMax. </p><ul><li>Recommended for medium to large rooms (300 - 600 sq. ft.)</li><li>Certified asthma and allergy-friendly by Asthma and Allergy Foundation of America</li><li>Removes particles as small as 0.3 microns</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>According to Amazon reviewers, this purifier functions better than expected and had really helped users combat their allergies and asthma. They no longer wake up with clogged sinus and that is a huge relief. One user even got 2 of this to cover more room.</p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Fellowes\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"9320501\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"9320501\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"25.13 X 16 X 8.13 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"12.2 X 18 X 28 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"12.5 Pound\"}]',0.00,167.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/AeraMax-Purifier-Allergy-4-Stage-Purification/dp/B00D8Y1YNC%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00D8Y1YNC','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4.5,\"counter\":157,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/AeraMax-Purifier-Allergy-4-Stage-Purification\\/dp\\/B00D8Y1YNC?tag=ideaing07-20\"}]','0