	(1565,134,'B00XCVV8CS','','Aiza Coronado','ZEN Thermostat - White','zen-thermostat-white','<p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">If you like simple thermostats that easy to operate, the Zen is the one you\'re looking for. It has this simple interface with a LED screen that displays simple feedback with icons appearing only if required. If you are a minimalist, you will absolutely fall in love with the design -- too perfect for your modern living. This white one looks clean and sophisticated, but if you\'re for darker shades, you can pick out the <a href=\"https://ideaing.com/product/zen-thermostat\" target=\"\">black one</a>.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Despite its simplicity, it is able to connect with SmartThings, Zigbee platform, SwannOne, and Securifi Almond/+ for scheduled operations, remote controlling, and more. </p><ul style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li>With an LED Screen display</li><li>Simple and easy to use</li><li>Can be connected to other smart devices</li></ul><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Amazon customer reviewers find the Zen Thermostat excellent; it has a 4.6-star rating. One user recommends getting it, especially if you already have a compatible home automation system in place. There were no problems encountered during installation, set-up and operation as the online install guide is super helpful.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Zen\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"Zen-01-W\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"0.88 X 4.3 X 4.3 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"2.5 X 6.7 X 7.1 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.9 Pound\"}]',199.00,199.00,1,'http://www.amazo