	(1566,123,'B00VYCYSF6','','Aiza Coronado','Sengled Boost Dimmable LED Bulb with Integrated Wi-Fi Repeater','sengled-boost-dimmable-led-bulb','<div></div><p>What if you can have a smart bulb that can also boost up your Wi-Fi signal? That\'s superb, right? Well, here it is, the Sengled Boost Dimmable LED Bulb with Integrated Wi-Fi Repeater. Let\'s talk about how it can help you personalize your lighting first. With an illumination of 550 Lumens, the bulb is dimmable as a single unit or as a group. Control it using an app that you can install for free on your smartphone or tablet. </p><p>As for its Wi-Fi Repeater function, it can eliminate dead spots in your home. Its range extends up to 100 feet with near line-of-sight.</p><div><br/></div><ul><li>&#65279;High efficiency, dimmable LED light</li><li>Range is 100 feet</li><li>Also available in A19, BR30, and PAR38</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>According to users, it is easy to set one up and it is pretty bright. As for the connectivity, it absolutely boosts their Wi-Fi signal. One user has used it with his Comcast XFinity and had no problems using it. However, there were a number of users who can\'t seem to connect their devices to the bulbs continuously. </p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"LexiLED Lighting (dba Sengled USA)\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"A01-A60NAE26CL\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"A01-A60NAE26CL\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"2.36 X 2.36 X 4.65 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"3.3 X 3.4 X 5.9 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"1 Pound\"}]',49.99,39.84,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Sengled-Boost-Dimmable-Integrated-Repeater/dp/B00VYCYSF6%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00VYCYSF6','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"NaN\",\"counter\":0},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":3,\"counter\":33,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Sengled-Boost-Dimmable-Integrated-Repeater\\/dp\\/B00VYCYSF6?tag=ideaing07-20\"}]','0','','1','','Inactive','Sengled Boost Dimmable LED Bulb Reviews and Deals','Sengled Boost Dimmable LED Bulb will not only let you personalize your lighting, but will extend your Wi-Fi signal with its repeater too. Ideaing provides aggregated reviews and lowest price on Sengled Boost Dimmable LED Bulb.','\"\"','Usually ships in 24 hours','2016-07-26 02:07:04','2016-07-26 02:26:10'),
	(1567,128,'B00GM7V8I8','','Aiza Coronado','Samsung SmartThings Arrival Sensor','samsung-smartthings-arrival-sensor','<div></div><p>Be alerted when a family member or a pet approaches or leaves a specified area at home with the Samsung SmartThings Arrival Sensor. This trigger can be connected to your smart home devices via the Samsung SmartThings Hub so you can program appropriate actions. You can choose to turn on the lights and unlock the door when they arrive or turn it off when they leave. Imagine all the possibilities that you can do given this sensor and your existing smart home devices. Make it work for your convenience and advantage. </p><p><br/></p><ul><li>Get notifications when somebody arrives or leaves </li><li>Can be used as a trigger to your other smart home devices</li><li>Attach it to your keys or place it in your bag</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>The Amazon reviews of this Samsung SmartThings Arrival Sensor are mixed. There are people who were satisfied, saying that the sensor worked as advertised and they have seamlessly integrated it into their smart home automation. Others, on the other hand, were saying that they encountered connectivity issues and the sensors get disconnected often.</p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"SmartThings\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"STSS-PRES-001\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"DHF-01517\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"1.9 X 0.46 X 0.98 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"2.2 X 3.6 X 3.8 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.01 Pound\"}]',29.99,27.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Samsung-SmartThings-STSS-PRES-001-Arrival-Sensor/dp/B00GM7V8I8%3FSubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00GM7V8I8','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"3.50\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":3,\"counter\":122,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Samsung-SmartThin