	(1568,116,'B00J05QFNW','','Aiza Coronado','D-Link Wireless AC750 Dual-Band Gigabit Router','d-link-wireless-ac750-gigabit-router','<div></div><p>The D-Link Wireless AC750 Dual-Band Gigabit Router is a 750Mbps Home Cloud App-enabled router that will give you reliable coverage. It has a dual band performance, which enables fast wireless speed for maximum throughput. You can finally binge watch Netflix or immerse in your gaming in total peace. What\'s great about this router is that you can manage and control using an app. The app also guides you during the setup and installation.</p><div></div><p><br/></p><ul><li>Offers 4 wired Gigabit Ethernet ports</li><li>Available in 4 different colors: Teal, White, Red, and Black</li><li>Preset security with advanced WPA2 encryption</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>There\'s a divided opinion on this router basing on the Amazon reviews. Others claim that it works effectively with stable connections, especially for those who are living in a small apartment. There were dissatisfied users, saying that it has spotty signal and had a hard time during the installation.</p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"D-Link\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"DIR-818LW\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"DIR-818LW\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"White\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"4.05 X 4.92 X 8.5 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"5.3 X 6.1 X 8.8 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"1.17 Pound\"}]',0.00,67.39,1,'http://www.amazon.com/D-Link-Wireless-App-Enabled-Dual-Band-DIR-818LW/dp/B00J05QFNW%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB00J05QFNW','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"2.50\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":3.5,\"counter\":71,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/D-Link-Wireless-App-Enabled-Dual-Band-DIR-818LW\\/dp\\/B00J05QFNW?tag=ideaing07-20\"},{\"key\":\"CNET\",\"value\":2.5,\"link\":