	(1569,123,'B01C5C9ZLK','','Aiza Coronado','Philips 455295 Hue White A19 LED Bulb (2 Pack)','philips-455295-hue-white-a19-led-bulb','<div></div><p>Here\'s another addition to your Philips Hue home lighting automation, the 2-pack Philips 455295 Hue White A19 LED Bulb. Each bulb blankets your space with 800 lumens of brightness and 2700k of soft warm light. Just like the other Hue bulbs, you can brighten or dim these bulbs according to your preference. It can retrofit into your medium-base table lamps, pendants, and other lighting fixtures that you have at home.</p><p><br/></p><ul><li>Connects to the Hue Bridge</li><li>Schedule or program their function through the Hue app</li><li>No rewiring needed</li></ul><p><br/></p><p>This is another Philips Hue bulb that Amazon customers love. According to them, they find it easy to use with Echo. It\'s fun and really lives up to the hype. One user encountered bulbs that didn\'t work, but they were replaced promptly. </p>','[{\"key\":\"Manufacturer\",\"value\":\"Philips Lighting\"},{\"key\":\"Model\",\"value\":\"455295\"},{\"key\":\"Part Number\",\"value\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Color\",\"value\":\"\"},{\"key\":\"Product Size\",\"value\":\"2.4 X 2.4 X 4.21 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Package Size\",\"value\":\"4 X 6.2 X 6.4 Inches\"},{\"key\":\"Weight\",\"value\":\"0.91 Pound\"}]',29.99,29.99,1,'http://www.amazon.com/Philips-455295-White-Equivalent-Single/dp/B01C5C9ZLK%3Fpsc%3D1%26SubscriptionId%3DAKIAIQYICLTUI4NBTPGA%26tag%3Dideaing07-20%26linkCode%3Dxm2%26camp%3D2025%26creative%3D165953%26creativeASIN%3DB01C5C9ZLK','','[{\"key\":\"Average\",\"value\":\"4.75\",\"counter\":2},{\"key\":\"Amazon\",\"value\":4.5,\"counter\":335,\"link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.com\\/Philips-455295-White-Equivalent-Single\\/dp\\/B01C5C9ZLK?tag=ideaing07-20\"},{\"key\":\"Walmart\",\"value\":4.5,\"link\":\"http:\\/\\/www.walmart.com\\/ip\\/Philips-455295-Philips-Hue-White-A19-Single-Bulb-with-WDK\\/47391662\",\"counter\":1},{\"key\":\"BestBuy\",\"value\":5,\"link